{"tid":1977553,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"4點鐘許SIR退休　寄語「隧道出口一定有光明」","createTime":"2020-04-18T05:04:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-18T06:06:39.000Z","uid":297241,"like":0,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ef2c6114d41b74bf27fe3163dae1f5b2afcb85d0","tid":1977553,"uid":297241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T05:04:52.000Z","msg":"4點鐘許SIR退休　<br />\n寄語「隧道出口一定有光明」<br />\n<br />\n79天佔中期間，時任警察公共關係科總警司、被網民稱呼為「4點鐘許SIR」的許鎮德共出席33次記者會，《放學ICU》等兒童節目亦要讓路；即將由助理處長（資訊系統）退下來的他笑言，要為「霸咗卡通時段」向小朋友講聲「唔好意思」。回顧31年半的警務生涯，許鎮德坦言，這段時間最漫長、艱辛及疲憊，但他認為，只要不放棄，「隧道出口一定有光明」，<span style=\"color: red;\">寄語同事用心工作，克盡己任，便可贏得市民信任及尊重。</span>"},{"pid":"77d2e6a0bd337515752bb1e9d0aa57d095934cfc","tid":1977553,"uid":2054,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T05:10:51.000Z","msg":"黑盡幾任？"},{"pid":"c3e9cb9058a7c0ea18fe0063152ec0defa8f9a83","tid":1977553,"uid":25260,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T05:12:06.000Z","msg":"去咗九巴做，un un 腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3405e04b9577ad1d955b2b8f876e37376d783f44","tid":1977553,"uid":151525,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T05:52:45.000Z","msg":"雖然狗還狗 起碼個人有公關<br />\n而家嘅狗 做嘢核核突突"},{"pid":"0d6c1dfb2efa078f73d2dc07995e551b037ebf30","tid":1977553,"uid":210253,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3405e04b9577ad1d955b2b8f876e37376d783f44","tid":1977553,"uid":151525,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T05:52:45.000Z","msg":"雖然狗還狗 起碼個人有公關<br />\n而家嘅狗 做嘢核核突突"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T05:53:52.000Z","msg":"拎大學生同毅進仔比"},{"pid":"b358392a6d45570dc0c4ae7f4f3cab2875d39a20","tid":1977553,"uid":12554,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T05:55:40.000Z","msg":"隧道？黑洞黎㗎喎"},{"pid":"99461d293118ef21bd2c89f055191828e2508fa3","tid":1977553,"uid":77533,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3405e04b9577ad1d955b2b8f876e37376d783f44"